#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.80"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.80:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.80:0.2"
msgid "8. Yodhājīvavagga"
msgstr "8. Warriors"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.80:0.3"
msgid "80. Catutthaanāgatabhayasutta"
msgstr "80. Future Perils (4th)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.80:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, anāgatabhayāni etarahi asamuppannāni āyatiṃ "
"samuppajjissanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, these five future perils have not currently arisen, but they "
"will arise in the future."

msgctxt "an5.80:1.2"
msgid "Tāni vo paṭibujjhitabbāni;"
msgstr "You should look out for them"

msgctxt "an5.80:1.3"
msgid "paṭibujjhitvā ca tesaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr "and try to give them up."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.80:2.1"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.80:2.2"
msgid "Bhavissanti, bhikkhave, bhikkhū anāgatamaddhānaṃ cīvare kalyāṇakāmā."
msgstr "In a future time there will be mendicants who like nice robes."

msgctxt "an5.80:2.3"
msgid ""
"Te cīvare kalyāṇakāmā samānā riñcissanti paṃsukūlikattaṃ, riñcissanti "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni;"
msgstr ""
"They will neglect the practice of wearing rag robes and the practice of "
"frequenting remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest."

msgctxt "an5.80:2.4"
msgid ""
"gāmanigamarājadhānīsu osaritvā vāsaṃ kappessanti, cīvarahetu ca anekavihitaṃ "
"anesanaṃ appatirūpaṃ āpajjissanti."
msgstr ""
"They will come down to the villages, towns, and capital cities and make "
"their homes there. And they will try to get robes in many kinds of wrong and "
"inappropriate ways."

msgctxt "an5.80:2.5"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamaṃ anāgatabhayaṃ etarahi asamuppannaṃ āyatiṃ "
"samuppajjissati."
msgstr ""
"This is the first future peril that has not currently arisen, but will arise "
"in the future …"

msgctxt "an5.80:2.6"
msgid "Taṃ vo paṭibujjhitabbaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.80:2.7"
msgid "paṭibujjhitvā ca tassa pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.109"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.80:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhavissanti bhikkhū anāgatamaddhānaṃ piṇḍapāte "
"kalyāṇakāmā."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, in a future time there will be mendicants who like nice alms-"
"food."

msgctxt "an5.80:3.2"
msgid ""
"Te piṇḍapāte kalyāṇakāmā samānā riñcissanti piṇḍapātikattaṃ, riñcissanti "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni;"
msgstr ""
"They will neglect the practice of walking for alms-food and the practice of "
"frequenting remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest."

msgctxt "an5.80:3.3"
msgid ""
"gāmanigamarājadhānīsu osaritvā vāsaṃ kappessanti jivhaggena rasaggāni "
"pariyesamānā, piṇḍapātahetu ca anekavihitaṃ anesanaṃ appatirūpaṃ "
"āpajjissanti."
msgstr ""
"They will come down to the villages, towns, and capital cities and make "
"their homes there. And they will try to get alms-food in many kinds of wrong "
"and inappropriate ways."

msgctxt "an5.80:3.4"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyaṃ anāgatabhayaṃ etarahi asamuppannaṃ āyatiṃ "
"samuppajjissati."
msgstr ""
"This is the second future peril that has not currently arisen, but will "
"arise in the future …"

msgctxt "an5.80:3.5"
msgid "Taṃ vo paṭibujjhitabbaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.80:3.6"
msgid "paṭibujjhitvā ca tassa pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.80:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhavissanti bhikkhū anāgatamaddhānaṃ senāsane "
"kalyāṇakāmā."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, in a future time there will be mendicants who like nice "
"lodgings."

#. VAR: rukkhamūlikattaṃ → āraññakattaṃ (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an5.80:4.2"
msgid ""
"Te senāsane kalyāṇakāmā samānā riñcissanti rukkhamūlikattaṃ, riñcissanti "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni;"
msgstr ""
"They will neglect the practice of staying at the root of a tree and the "
"practice of frequenting remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest."

msgctxt "an5.80:4.3"
msgid ""
"gāmanigamarājadhānīsu osaritvā vāsaṃ kappessanti, senāsanahetu ca "
"anekavihitaṃ anesanaṃ appatirūpaṃ āpajjissanti."
msgstr ""
"They will come down to the villages, towns, and capital cities and make "
"their homes there. And they will try to get lodgings in many kinds of wrong "
"and inappropriate ways."

msgctxt "an5.80:4.4"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyaṃ anāgatabhayaṃ etarahi asamuppannaṃ āyatiṃ "
"samuppajjissati."
msgstr ""
"This is the third future peril that has not currently arisen, but will arise "
"in the future …"

msgctxt "an5.80:4.5"
msgid "Taṃ vo paṭibujjhitabbaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.80:4.6"
msgid "paṭibujjhitvā ca tassa pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

# See discussion here: https://discourse.suttacentral.net/t/should-monks-beware-of-living-with-novices/2257
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.80:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhavissanti bhikkhū anāgatamaddhānaṃ "
"bhikkhunīsikkhamānāsamaṇuddesehi saṃsaṭṭhā viharissanti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, in a future time there will be mendicants who mix closely with "
"nuns, female interns, and female novices."

msgctxt "an5.80:5.2"
msgid ""
"Bhikkhunīsikkhamānāsamaṇuddesehi saṃsagge kho pana, bhikkhave, sati etaṃ "
"pāṭikaṅkhaṃ:"
msgstr "In such conditions, it can be expected that"

msgctxt "an5.80:5.3"
msgid ""
"‘anabhiratā vā brahmacariyaṃ carissanti, aññataraṃ vā saṅkiliṭṭhaṃ āpattiṃ "
"āpajjissanti, sikkhaṃ vā paccakkhāya hīnāyāvattissanti’."
msgstr ""
"they will live the spiritual life dissatisfied, or commit one of the corrupt "
"offences, or reject the training and return to a lesser life."

msgctxt "an5.80:5.4"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ, bhikkhave, catutthaṃ anāgatabhayaṃ etarahi asamuppannaṃ āyatiṃ "
"samuppajjissati."
msgstr ""
"This is the fourth future peril that has not currently arisen, but will "
"arise in the future …"

msgctxt "an5.80:5.5"
msgid "Taṃ vo paṭibujjhitabbaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.80:5.6"
msgid "paṭibujjhitvā ca tassa pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.110"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.80:6.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhavissanti bhikkhū anāgatamaddhānaṃ "
"ārāmikasamaṇuddesehi saṃsaṭṭhā viharissanti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, in a future time there will be mendicants who mix closely with "
"monastery attendants and novices."

msgctxt "an5.80:6.2"
msgid ""
"Ārāmikasamaṇuddesehi saṃsagge kho pana, bhikkhave, sati etaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ:"
msgstr "In such conditions it can be expected that"

msgctxt "an5.80:6.3"
msgid ""
"‘anekavihitaṃ sannidhikāraparibhogaṃ anuyuttā viharissanti, oḷārikampi "
"nimittaṃ karissanti, pathaviyāpi haritaggepi’."
msgstr ""
"they will engage in storing up goods for their own enjoyment, and making "
"obvious hints about digging the earth and cutting plants."

msgctxt "an5.80:6.4"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamaṃ anāgatabhayaṃ etarahi asamuppannaṃ āyatiṃ "
"samuppajjissati."
msgstr ""
"This is the fifth future peril that has not currently arisen, but will arise "
"in the future …"

msgctxt "an5.80:6.5"
msgid "Taṃ vo paṭibujjhitabbaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.80:6.6"
msgid "paṭibujjhitvā ca tassa pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.80:7.1"
msgid ""
"Imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca anāgatabhayāni etarahi asamuppannāni āyatiṃ "
"samuppajjissanti."
msgstr ""
"These are the five future perils that have not currently arisen, but will "
"arise in the future."

msgctxt "an5.80:7.2"
msgid "Tāni vo paṭibujjhitabbāni;"
msgstr "You should look out for them"

msgctxt "an5.80:7.3"
msgid "paṭibujjhitvā ca tesaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabban”ti."
msgstr "and try to give them up.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.80:7.4"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.80:7.5"
msgid "Yodhājīvavaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.80:8.1"
msgid "Dve cetovimuttiphalā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.80:8.2"
msgid "dve ca dhammavihārino;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.80:8.3"
msgid "Yodhājīvā ca dve vuttā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.80:8.4"
msgid "cattāro ca anāgatāti."
msgstr ""
